QuestData.Title: Hero's Call: Blade's Edge Mountains!
QuestData.Description: The Alliance forces of Sylvanaar in the Blade's Edge Mountains require reinforcements.$b$bThe King has asked for any able bodied members of the Alliance to journey to the mountains along the northern border of Zangarmarsh.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Rina Moonspring at Sylvanaar in the Blade's Edge Mountains.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Rina Moonspring at Sylvanaar in the Blade's Edge Mountains.
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you for coming. We could use more able bodies.
